==Description==

La commande [[Image:Fasteners_Search.svg|24px]] '''Fasteners Rechercher''' affiche une boîte de dialogue permettant de rechercher et d'insérer des fixations par leur nom ou leur description.

[[Image:Fasteners_Search_Dialog.png|350px]]
{{Caption|Le panneau des tâches de la commande}}

<span id="Usage"></span>
==Utilisation==

Pour obtenir des instructions générales d'utilisation, consultez [[Fasteners_Workbench/fr#Utilisation|atelier Fasteners]].

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# There are several ways to invoke the command:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:Fasteners_Search.svg|16px]] [[Fasteners_Search|Search Fasteners]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Fasteners → [[Image:Fasteners_Search.svg|16px]] Search Fasteners}} option from the menu.
# The {{MenuCommand|Search Fasteners}} dialog box opens.
# Enter a search term in the input box at the top. At least 2 characters are required.
# The list of search results updates as more characters are entered.
# Select a fastener from the list.
# Press the {{Button|Insert Fastener}} button.
# The dialog is modeless, meaning it can stay open while you continue working in FreeCAD.
# Optionally press the {{Button|Close}} button to close the dialog box.
</div>


